		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p><strong>Ready for your next challenge? Lead a team of young people on overseas development projects with Restless Development.</strong><br>
			Do something amazing this autumn. Apply to be a Team Leader on the fuly funded International Citizen Service programme. You'll be overseas for 12 weeks, leading a team of enthusiastic and passionate young people on development projects in communities across Africa and Asia. Learn new skills and develop ones you already have, all while engaging in a truly life-changing placement.</p>

<p>Deadlines throughout July, departures throughout September and October.</p>

<p>Head to the <a href="http://restlessdevelopment.org/ics-team-leaders"target="_blank">Restless Development website</a> to find out more.<br>
			<br>
						
			</td><td align="right" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/restless%20development%20logo.JPG" alt="" width="200" height="" border="0"></td>
			
